      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature high-revving individual throttle bodies. This example benefits from a recently serviced double-VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring structural rigidity under high-torque loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the chassis's celebrated communicative feedback. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, its thermal management and valvetrain clearances are strictly within spec.",
